title: 2020 CFB Pick Em Week 12
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco are back for another week of picks. Tensions are high as Rico had a scheduling conflict due to an interview for the Bench Mob podcast!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
